了「教学型特聘教授」岗位，今年对这一岗位内容进行进一步补充，单设指标、独立评审、单独考核，为潜心一线教学和教改研究的教师开通晋升直通车。在职称评定中，对于重大标志性成果特别是实现基础理论研究领域重大突破和被行业广泛应用的颠覆性技术等，经领域内5名以上二级教授联名推荐，可直接提交高级职称评审委员会审定，不受任职年限、论文、项目等量化成果的数量限制，切实为培育重大创新成果和培养高端人才提供制度保障。 在会上，副校长郝海平说了这样一句话： 「我们将为高水平人才开辟绿色通道，大家只要有能说得出来的成果，并得到别人的认可，就能以提名推荐的方式参加正高职称评审，你们甚至可以潜心研究 10 年不发论文。」国自然交流：动真格！这所高校霸气官宣：可潜心研究10年不发论文！"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ip8LWpNuF2JMqEAMaCDc2NTQ3NTY4IKmM3Y8GMBI42gNAI3IJNTE0MTk3NDc2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-62abbcf1f0cfe5928f64e02a6c5501f1_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"36_1643656106.6986027","card_id":"Q_512170914","target":{"id":512170914,"title":"职场人原地过年，如何才能更有年味儿仪式感？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/512170914","type":"question","created":1642493925,"answer_count":39,"follower_count":80,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1400,2566,152575,709460,1884365],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4Ip8LWpNuF2JMqEAMaCDc2MDk3MzczIOXvmY8GMAE4UEAkcgk1MTIxNzA5MTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-396ccfc4954d34997a4965a6c52ab49f_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"37_1643656106.699038","card_id":"Q_512755204","target":{"id":512755204,"title":"2022 春节档预售《水门桥》票房一骑绝尘，它会是今年的票房冠军吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/512755204","type":"question","created":1642769969,"answer_count":191,"follower_count":355,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[68,26606,1437271,1884365,1891059],"comment_count":47,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8