出现在去年12月，原始奥密克戎毒株开始传播不久便出现了。据报道，BA.2缺少一个关键突变，这可能使其更难追踪。科学家们认为，它可能更具传播性，并且更难与其他变体区分开来。 UKHSA表示，在其他约40个国家也发现了感染BA.2变异株的病例，占印度、丹麦和瑞典等一些国家最新病例的大部分。尽管在英国，奥密克戎毒株BA.1变体目前仍占主导地位，但感染BA.2变体的病例仍在增加。 世卫组织强调，病毒基因组变化的情况仍存在不确定性，需要进行监测，因为最近几天的病例显示，BA.2变体导致的发病率急剧上升，特别是在印度和丹麦。 法国流行病学家安托万·弗拉欧说：“令我们惊讶的是，这种在亚洲广泛传播的亚型病毒在丹麦流行的速度如此之快。”英国正调查奥密克戎亚变体毒株：传播快但毒力弱_病例_丹麦_病毒"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ip8LWpNuF2JMqEAMaCDc2MzkwNTgwIL32w48GMAg4ywJALHIJNTEzNDkwOTc4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c60a77913dc8f3c97f9678880cd16975_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"45_1643656106.7026896","card_id":"Q_513423431","target":{"id":513423431,"title":"为什么其他生物看到同类尸体不会害怕，而人类看到同类的尸体会害怕?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/513423431","type":"question","created":1643132138,"answer_count":187,"follower_count":681,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[507,1571,8437,17729,89475],"comment_count":25,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Ip8LWpNuF2JMqEAMaCDc2Mzc1NTk5IOrpwI8GMBk4qQVALXIJNTEzNDIzNDMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-2acd2528bbddd005a208b638461832e8_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"46_1643656106.7032616","card_id":"Q_513701747","target":{"id":513701747,"title":"你收藏了哪些 2022 年的春节祝福文案？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/513701747","type":"question","created":1643289556,"answer_count":47,"follower_count":136,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[9014,105508,285235,717140,1884365],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_inf